<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>AFC G-07913R - Replace Existing Crankcase Breather System with a Heated Breather System</stitle>
    <afc id="afc07913">
        <afcnum>G-07913R</afcnum>
        <afcdate>November, 2007</afcdate>
        <subjectfile>Engine</subjectfile>
        <subject>Replace Existing Crankcase Breather System with a Heated Breather System</subject>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <truckmodelgroup/>

                <truckmodel>CF 500
                    <daterange>
                        <startdate>08/04/2004</startdate>
                        <enddate>08/21/2007</enddate>
                    </daterange>
                </truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>CF 600
                    <daterange>
                        <startdate>08/04/2004</startdate>
                        <enddate>08/21/2007</enddate>
                    </daterange>
                </truckmodel>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>Replace breather assembly to eliminate freezing problems in severe cold climates.</para>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>This campaign is VIN specific based on application and geographic location. If you have
                            units involved, your International service representative (CSE) will have already notified
                            you and provided the information needed to acquire parts to complete this AFC.
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>Ensure AFC 06914 or AFC 06915 has been completed on the truck before proceeding with this
                            repair.
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
                <para>For further instructions, refer to
                    <exhotlnk
                            document="https://evalue.internationaldelivers.com/service_kb/iKNow/Document_Viewer.aspx?Control_ID=1116"
                            bookname="EXTERNAL">iKNow article IK1200179
                    </exhotlnk>
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
        <partsinfo id="t069091">
            <table id="t0791301" tblwidth="pg-wide">
                <tgroup cols="3" align="center">
                    <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="0.84*"/>
                    <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="1.26*"/>
                    <colspec colname="col3" colwidth="0.90*"/>
                    <thead>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Part number</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Description</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Quantity</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>1882600C91 (2005 and 2006)</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Heated Breather Kit</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>1 kit per vehicle</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
            <para>Please note, you only need one kit per engine. If you have a 2005 or 2006 engine, you need kit number
                1882600C91. Instructions for this AFC have been included with the parts kits.
            </para>
            <para>Please complete all involved units as soon as possible so they will have the heated breather installed
                before severe cold weather arrives.
            </para>
        </partsinfo>
        <laborinfo>
            <para>Operation number must appear on all claims.</para>
            <table id="t0691302" tblwidth="pg-wide">
                <title>Labor Information</title>
                <tgroup cols="3">
                    <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="1.69in"/>
                    <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="2.38in"/>
                    <colspec colname="col3" colwidth="1.32in"/>
                    <thead>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1" align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Operation No.</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2" align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Description</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3" align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Time</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1" align="center">
                                <para>A40-07913-1</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>Replace Breather Kit</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3" align="center">
                                <para>0.9 Hr.</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
        </laborinfo>
        <claims>
            <para>
                <title>ADMINISTRATIVE PROCEDURE</title>
            </para>
            <para>Expense is to be charged to Warranty.
                <hotlnk xrefid="afclaim">Claims</hotlnk>
                are to be submitted in the normal manner, making reference to Authorized Field Change Number G-07913.
            </para>
            <para>It is important that the coding be completed properly to assist in processing the warranty claim.
                Complete instructions will be found in the Warranty Manual, Section 7-1. Special attention should be
                given to Items 39 through 44.
            </para>
            <para>To assure this important improvement is made in a timely manner, all claims for G-07913 activity must
                be submitted by November 30, 2008 or within the normal warranty period for the vehicle, if after
                November 30, 2008.
            </para>
            <figure id="afclaim" figsize="pg-wide">
